Dowload 2020-10-08
-----------------------------------------
wget https://fsl.fmrib.ox.ac.uk/fsldownloads/fsl-6.0.4-sources.tar.gz
wget https://www.vtk.org/files/release/7.1/VTK-7.1.1.tar.gz

md5sums:
